The '''Meeknu clan''' was a [[Jawa/Legends|Jawa]] family transplanted from [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] to [[Raxus Prime/Legends|Raxus Prime]] prior to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] to operate the heavy machinery there.

